、勇气和天才，就不可能得到认可。如果说我对他们没有在各自类别中获得提名感到失望，那是轻描淡写的。”</p><p>他继续说道：“尽管困难重重，除了几个没有灵魂、衣着暴露、值得庆幸的是没有开裆的娃娃，她们让我们开怀大笑，她们伤了我们的心，她们推动了文化，她们创造了历史。他们的工作应该与其他非常值得提名的人一起得到认可。”</p><p>高斯林在结束声明时写道：“话虽如此，我为亚美莉卡·费雷拉和其他令人难以置信的艺术家感到高兴，他们贡献了自己的才华，使这部电影成为如此具有开创性的电影。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hillary-clinton-spectacularly-mocked-for-barbie-oscars-snub-tweet-3576426">希拉里·克林顿 (Hillary Clinton) 因对芭比奥斯卡奖的冷落而受到极大嘲笑的推文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Bleachers 的杰克·安东诺夫分享了《The New Look》配乐的详细信息https://www.nme.com/news/music/bleachers-jack-antonoff-shares-details-of-soundtrack-to-the-new-look-3576431?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bleachers-jack-antonoff-新外观配乐细节分享Alex RigottiWed, 24 Jan 2024 19:53:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3576431 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰克·安东诺夫（Christopher Polk/Penske Media via Getty Images 摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Florence + The Machine、Lana Del Rey、The 1975、Beabadoobee、Nick Cave 和 Perfume Genius 都计划出现</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bleachers-jack-antonoff-shares-details-of-soundtrack-to-the-new-look-3576431">Bleachers 乐队的 Jack Antonoff 分享《The New Look》配乐细节的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰克·安东诺夫（Christopher Polk/Penske Media via Getty Images 摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jack-Antonoff-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫</a>透露了即将推出的电视节目“The New Look”的众星云集的配乐。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/bleachers-jack-antonoff-cover-interview-2021-take-the-sadness-out-of-saturday-night-3006942">Bleachers：“这张专辑是关于想要保持快乐，而不是理解为什么你不能”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a>主唱宣布他是 Apple TV 即将推出的系列节目的制片人，该系列节目将涵盖 10 集。该原声带将是安东诺夫的新厂牌 Shadow of the City 的第一张专辑，该厂<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-signs-with-dirty-hit-announces-new-venture-with-the-1975-manager-jamie-oborne-3486106">牌是 Dirty Hit 的印记</a>。</p><p>现在，安东诺夫公布了原声带的所有嘉宾，其中将包括二十世纪早期至中期歌曲的翻唱。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beabadobee">Beabadoobee</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">Nick Cave</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/perfume-genius">Perfume Genius</a>都将亮相。</p><p>该原声带的第一首单曲“White Cliffs of Dover”（由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-and-the-machine">Florence + The Machine</a>创作）将于 1 月 31 日发行。该原声带的发行日期尚未确定。</p><p>查看下面的完整曲目列表： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="新面貌——官方预告片|苹果电视+" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lXN5Ws7LxkA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h3> <strong>“The New Look”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1. 佛罗伦萨+机器——“多佛白色悬崖”</strong><br /> <strong>2. 1975年——“现在就是时候”</strong><br /> <strong>3. 拉娜·德雷——《蓝天》</strong><br /> <strong>4.香水天才——“一天有什么不同”</strong><br /> <strong>5.尼克·凯夫——《玫瑰人生》</strong><br /> <strong>6. Beabadoobee – “这只是一个纸月亮”</strong><br /> <strong>7. 乔伊·奥拉多昆——《我向月亮许愿》</strong><br /> <strong>8. Bartees Strange – “你总是伤害你所爱的人”</strong><br /> <strong>9. Sam Dew——“我覆盖海滨”</strong><br /> <strong>10. Bleachers——“几乎就像恋爱一样”</strong></p><p>这部历史剧的前三集将于 2 月 14 日上映，本·门德尔森 (Ben Mendelsohn) 饰演克里斯汀·迪奥 (Christian Dior)，朱丽叶·比诺什 (Juliette Binoche) 饰演可可·香奈儿 (Coco Chanel)，这两位标志性时装设计师将在二战中奋勇前进。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maisie-williams">麦茜·威廉姆斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-interviews/john-malkovich-interview-space-force-2676884">约翰·马尔科维奇</a>、艾米莉·莫迪默、克拉斯·邦和格伦·克洛斯也已宣布成为演员。</p><p>安东诺夫还计划于 3 月 8 日发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bleachers-team-up-with-lana-del-rey-on-alma-mater-and-announce-new-self-titled-album-3540254">Bleachers 的同名专辑。</a>乐队将在选定的日期在英国进行巡演 - 请参阅下面的内容并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/bleachers-tickets/artist/1965170?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=WyQS5CymqxyNU6mQdCxfu1IQUkHzFdV8CzQSXE0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559">在此处</a>获取门票。</p><p> <strong>2024 年 3 月</strong><br /><strong>19 – 伦敦，O2 论坛肯特镇</strong><br /><strong>22 - 曼彻斯特，O2 Ritz</strong><br /> <strong>23 – 伯明翰，O2 研究所</strong><br /><strong>25 – 格拉斯哥，SWG3 镀锌机</strong></p><p>在其他新闻中，安东诺夫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-reveals-which-taylor-swift-song-deeply-impacted-him-3561348">谈到了一首对他影响深远的泰勒·斯威夫特歌曲</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bleachers-jack-antonoff-shares-details-of-soundtrack-to-the-new-look-3576431">Bleachers 乐队的 Jack Antonoff 分享《The New Look》配乐细节的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)、杰米·T (Jamie T)、Snow Patrol 等人宣布出演《Y Not 2024》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-jamie-t-snow-patrol-and-more-for-y-not-2024-3576409?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=noel-gallagher-杰米·t·雪地巡逻队和更多 for-y-not-2024Alex Rigotti Wed, 24 Jan 2024 19:17:59 +0000 FestivalsMusic NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3576409 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)、杰米·T (Jamie T) 和加里·莱特博迪 (Gary Lightbody)/Snow Patrol（图片来源：Matt Crockett、Reuben Bastienne-Lewis 和 Roberto Ricciuti/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>音乐节将于 8 月 2 日至 4 日返回派克霍尔</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-jamie-t-snow-patrol-and-more-for-y-not-2024-3576409">Noel Gallagher、Jamie T、Snow Patrol 等人为 Y Not 2024 宣布的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)、杰米·T (Jamie T) 和加里·莱特博迪 (Gary Lightbody)/Snow Patrol（图片来源：Matt Crockett、Reuben Bastienne-Lewis 和 Roberto Ricciuti/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Y-Not-Festival-2024-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/y-not-festival">Y Not</a>公布了 2024 年第一波名字。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/noel-gallagher-live-in-london-oasis-setlist-3474962">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 伦敦现场演出：绿洲经典在重聚传闻中大放异彩</a></strong></li></ul><p>下一届音乐节将于 8 月 2 日至 4 日在德比郡派克霍尔举行。现在，它揭开了头条新闻，并宣布了一大波名字。您可以在 1 月 25 日下午 6 点<a href="https://mailchi.mp/bc65e7314936/8lonbwb0oa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>报名并购买预售票，而一般销售将于 1 月 26 日晚上 10 点<a href="https://ynotfestival.com/tickets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>开始。</p><p> 8 月 2 日， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snow-patrol">《Snow Patrol》</a>将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/two-snow-patrol-members-leave-amidst-hints-at-band-drama-3494407">在今年即将推出新专辑</a>的传言中成为头条新闻。第二天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-t">Jamie T</a>将登上舞台，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">Noel Gallagher 的 High Flying Birds</a>将为音乐节画上圆满的句号。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kaiser-chiefs">凯撒酋长队 (Kaiser Chiefs)</a>也将成为 8 月 1 日节前演出的主角。</p><p>其他宣布加入的乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kooks">The Kooks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/declan-mckenna">Declan McKenna</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-vaccines">The Vaccines</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jake-bugg">Jake Bugg</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-snuts">The Snuts</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">Frank Turner</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">Soft Play</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pale-waves">Pale Waves</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-b">Katy B。</a></p><p>今年崭露头角的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">English Teacher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-dad">NewDad</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hot-wax">Hot Wax</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleach-lab">Bleach Lab</a>也将在 Y Not 演出。查看下面的完整阵容： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2fgYaxN53x/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,